summary: This document is a police report detailing a summons issued to Ghislaine Maxwell for a parking violation at a bus stop in New York City. The report includes specifics about the vehicle involved and the circumstances of the violation.

locations: 358 El Brillo Way, Palm Beach, FL
keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell was issued a summons for parking in a bus stop.
The summons was issued on January 31, 2007.
The vehicle involved was a 2007 black Cadillac with the plate number T918XM.
The summons was issued by the New York City Police Department.
The report indicates the violation occurred at 15:46.
